    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >异世界的驱魔师大人</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370010/extras/9499c38be6b62e1cabd089fa60526001.poster.avif?t=1686006596\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370010/extras/9499c38be6b62e1cabd089fa60526001.webm?t=1686006596\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370010/extras/9499c38be6b62e1cabd089fa60526001.mp4?t=1686006596\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你扮演一个普通的搬砖人，意外穿越进入异世界，成为被女神选中的驱魔师。你拥有独特的驱魔技能：将魔王的瘴气实体化成为砖块，并发射法球到打破它们。使用你独特的驱魔技能，帮助被魔王附身的美少女驱魔，并最终打败魔王吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻松又具有策略性</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370010/extras/8c5b1aa12368d840e4493e1f93c3cc05.poster.avif?t=1686006596\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370010/extras/8c5b1aa12368d840e4493e1f93c3cc05.webm?t=1686006596\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370010/extras/8c5b1aa12368d840e4493e1f93c3cc05.mp4?t=1686006596\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>砖块具有不同的特殊属性，有的可以产生爆炸伤害周围的其他砖块，有的被击破后会分类成小的砖块，有的会吃掉你的法球！虽然游戏玩起来很轻松，但有时还是需要仔细思考，否则可能会陷入困境呢！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简单易用的编辑器</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370010/extras/94bff5e7762934ceb461e715ce9d114c.poster.avif?t=1686006596\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370010/extras/94bff5e7762934ceb461e715ce9d114c.webm?t=1686006596\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370010/extras/94bff5e7762934ceb461e715ce9d114c.mp4?t=1686006596\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>内置的编辑器简单易用，点点鼠标就能创建出有趣的关卡，快上传到创意工坊和大家分享你的关卡吧！",
